{
  "title": "Public notice: Public participation on CID by-law",
  "description": "BUSINESS NEWS - Notice...",
  "bodyText": "[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"text\":\"Sponsored Content\",\"html\":\"<span class=\\\"label label-danger label-sm\\\" style=\\\"border-radius: 0; margin-right: 2px;\\\">Sponsored Content</span>\"},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"text\":\"BUSINESS NEWS - Notice is hereby given in terms of Section 22 of the Municipal Property Rates Act (Act 6 of 2004) that the local community is invited to submit representations in connection with the Community Improvement District (CID) By-Law.\",\"html\":\"BUSINESS NEWS - <span data-contrast=\\\"auto\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\"><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">Notice is</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">hereby</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">given</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">in</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">terms</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">of </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">Section 22</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">of the</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">Municipal Property</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">Rates Act (Act 6</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">of</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">2004) that the local community is invited to </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">submit</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> representations in connection with the Community Improvement District (CID) By-Law. </span></span>\"},{\"type\":\"blockquote\",\"text\":\"The Dr. Beyers Naude Local Municipality invites interested parties to participate in the public participation process for the Community Improvement District (CID) By-Law.\"},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"text\":\"Members of the public can access the documents for public inspection on the municipal website www.bnlm.gov.za and at the following municipal offices and Libraries in Graaff Reinet, Aberdeen, Nieu Bethesda, Jansenville, Klipplaat, Rietbron, Steytlerville and Willowmore:\",\"html\":\"<span data-contrast=\\\"auto\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\"><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">Members</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">of</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">the</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">public</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">can</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">access</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">the</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">documents</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">for</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">public</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">inspection</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">on</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">the</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">municipal</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">website </span></span><a href=\\\"http://www.bnlm.gov.za/\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\"><span data-contrast=\\\"none\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\"><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">www.bnlm.gov.za</span></span></a><span data-contrast=\\\"none\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\"><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span></span><span data-contrast=\\\"auto\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\"><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">and</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">at</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">the</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">following</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">municipal</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">offices</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">and</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">Libraries</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">in</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">Graaff</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">Reinet,</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">Aberdeen, Nieu Bethesda, </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">Jansenville</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">, </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">Klipplaat</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">, </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">Rietbron</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">, </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">Steytlerville</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> and </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">Willowmore</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">:</span></span><span data-ccp-props=\\\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559685&quot;:338,&quot;335559737&quot;:382,&quot;335559738&quot;:37,&quot;335559740&quot;:276}\\\"> </span>\"},{\"type\":\"list\",\"items\":[\"Graaff-Reinet- 12-14 Caledon Street Graaff Reinet\",\"Steytlerville- Church Street Steytlerville\",\"Willowmore- 42 Main Street Willowmore\",\"Aberdeen- 17 Voortrekker Street Aberdeen\",\"Jansenville- 34 Mainstreet Jansenville\",\"Nieu-Bethesda- Muller Street Nieu-Bethesda\",\"Klipplaat- 53 Maxmamase Street Klipplaat\",\"Rietbron- 01 Keulder Street Rietbron\"],\"ordered\":false},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"text\":\"Written Comments may be directed to the Chief Financial Officer, Mr. Jimmy Joubert via email ([email protected]) or submitted to the Municipal Manager at P.O Box 71, Graaff-Reinet, 6280 not later than 21 days from the date of publication. For any enquiries feel free to contact the CFO on telephone number: (049) 807 5700 during office hours from 07h30 to 16h30.\",\"html\":\"<span data-contrast=\\\"auto\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\"><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">Written Comments may be directed to the Chief Financial Officer, Mr. Jimmy Joubert via email (</span></span><a href=\\\"/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#c3a9acb6a1a6b1b7a983a1adafaeeda4acb5edb9a2\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\"><span data-contrast=\\\"none\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\"><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"><span class=\\\"__cf_email__\\\" data-cfemail=\\\"8ae0e5ffe8eff8fee0cae8e4e6e7a4ede5fca4f0eb\\\">[email protected]</span></span></span><span data-contrast=\\\"auto\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\"><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">)</span></span></a><span data-contrast=\\\"auto\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\"><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span></span><span data-contrast=\\\"auto\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\"><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">or</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">submitted</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> to the Municipal Manager at P.O Box 71, Graaff-Reinet, 6280 not later</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">than </span></span><span data-contrast=\\\"auto\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\"><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">21</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">days from the</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">date</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">of</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">publication</span></span><span data-contrast=\\\"auto\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\"><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">. For any enquiries feel</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">free</span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">to contact the CFO on telephone number: </span></span><span data-contrast=\\\"auto\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\"><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">(049) 807 5700 </span></span><span data-contrast=\\\"auto\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\"><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">during office hours from </span></span><span data-contrast=\\\"auto\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\"><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">07h30 to 16h30</span></span><span data-contrast=\\\"auto\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\"><span data-ccp-parastyle=\\\"Body Text\\\">.</span></span><span data-ccp-props=\\\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:338,&quot;335559737&quot;:705,&quot;335559740&quot;:276}\\\"> </span><span data-ccp-props=\\\"{&quot;335559738&quot;:73}\\\"> </span>\"},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"text\":\"Municipal Manager - Dr E.M. Rankwana\",\"html\":\"Municipal Manager - <span data-contrast=\\\"auto\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\">Dr E.M. Rankwana</span><span data-ccp-props=\\\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:418,&quot;335559731&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:7597,&quot;335559738&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:271}\\\"> </span>\"},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"text\":\"Church Square PO Box 71 Graaff-Reinet Tel: 049 807 5700Fax: 049 892 4319 Email: [email protected] website www.bnlm.gov.za\",\"html\":\"<span data-contrast=\\\"auto\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\">Church Square </span><br><span data-contrast=\\\"auto\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\">PO Box 71 Graaff-Reinet</span><span data-ccp-props=\\\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:7950,&quot;335559731&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:382,&quot;335559738&quot;:166,&quot;335559740&quot;:283}\\\"> </span><br><span data-contrast=\\\"none\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\">Tel: 049 </span><span data-contrast=\\\"auto\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\">807 5700</span><br><span data-contrast=\\\"auto\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\">Fax: 049 892 4319</span><span data-ccp-props=\\\"{&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:7950,&quot;335559731&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:44}\\\"> </span><br><span data-contrast=\\\"auto\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\">Email: </span><a data-fr-linked=\\\"true\\\" href=\\\"/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#b1dcc4dfd8d2d8c1d0ddd8c5c8f1d3dfdddc9fd6dec79fcbd0\\\"><span class=\\\"__cf_email__\\\" data-cfemail=\\\"84e9f1eaede7edf4e5e8edf0fdc4e6eae8e9aae3ebf2aafee5\\\">[email protected]</span></a><span da